## What Are We Building?
**Sumita AI** вЂ” a developer tool that wraps any existing API with a Stellar micropayment layer using the x402 protocol. Developers earn USDC per API call automatically. No blockchain knowledge required from the developer.

---

## App Name
Always **Sumita AI** вЂ” never "SumitaAI", never "sumita", never "SUMITA AI"

## Tagline
**"The payment layer the internet was missing."**

---

## Tech Stack вЂ” Never Change This

### Frontend
- React (Vite)
- TailwindCSS
- Framer Motion (Sumita animations)
- Recharts (earnings chart)
- React Router (page navigation)

### Backend
- Node.js + Express
- @x402/express (x402 payment middleware)
- @stellar/stellar-sdk (wallet generation + transactions)
- better-sqlite3 (local database)
- cors, dotenv, uuid

### Blockchain
- Network: Stellar Testnet
- Token: USDC on Stellar
- Protocol: x402

